%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquantum-computing-cybersecurity-threat-break-encryption-cryptocurrency-bitcoin-blockchain-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EQuantum%20computing%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20rapidly%20evolving%20field%20of%20technology%20that%20combines%20the%20disciplines%20of%20computer%20science%2C%20math%2C%20and%20quantum%20mechanics%20to%20solve%20more%20complex%20calculations%20more%20quickly%20than%20is%20possible%20through%20classical%20computing.%20The%20foundation%20of%20quantum%20computing%20relies%20on%20units%20of%20information%20called%20qubits%2C%20rather%20than%20the%20binary%20bits%20used%20in%20classical%20computing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EQubits%20exist%20in%20multiple%20states%20at%20once%2C%20like%20a%20spinning%20coin%20appearing%20to%20show%20both%20heads%20and%20tails%20simultaneously.%20They%20behave%20differently%20when%20observed%2C%20and%20require%20specific%20conditions%20such%20as%20low%20light%20or%20extremely%20cold%20environments%20to%20replicate%20results%20reliably%20and%20without%20errors%2C%20which%20has%20made%20advancement%20in%20the%20field%20slowgoing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20when%20they%20behave%20predictably%20at%20a%20large%20enough%20scale%2C%20qubits%20enable%20quantum%20computers%20to%20quickly%20calculate%20equations%20with%20multiple%20solutions%20and%20perform%20advanced%20computations%20that%20would%20be%20impossible%20for%20classical%20computers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EResearchers%20in%20the%20field%20agree%20that%20computations%20solvable%20through%20quantum%20computing%20could%20help%20discover%20new%20drugs%2C%20promote%20sustainable%20food%20growth%20in%20harsh%20climates%2C%20and%20develop%20new%20chemical%20compounds%20that%20break%20down%20plastics%20or%20break%20our%20current%20encryption%20methods%2C%20among%20other%20outcomes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22youtube%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FwSHmygPQukQ%3Ffeature%3Doembed%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Majorana%201%20Explained%3A%20The%20Path%20to%20a%20Million%20Qubits%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3ENadella%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Esaid%20he%20believes%20quantum%20will%20be%20a%20global%20game%20changer%20when%20used%20in%20conjunction%20with%20advancements%20in%20artificial%20intelligence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20appearance%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D4GLSzuYXh6w%26ab_channel%3DDwarkeshPatel%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDwarkesh%20Podcast%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Nadella%20said%20quantum%20computing%20will%20be%20most%20useful%20for%20exploring%20how%20various%20compounds%20work%20in%20different%20states%2C%20like%20advancements%20in%20chemical%20physics%20and%20biology%2C%20rather%20than%20the%20data-heavy%20processing%20that%20AI%20is%20best%20at.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20way%20I%20think%20of%20it%20is%2C%20if%20you%20have%20AI%20plus%20quantum%2C%20maybe%20you'll%20use%20quantum%20to%20generate%20synthetic%20data%20that%20then%20gets%20used%20by%20AI%20to%20train%20better%20models%20that%20know%20how%20to%20model%20something%20like%20chemistry%20or%20physics%20or%20what%20have%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20Nadella%20said%20in%20the%20podcast.%20%26quot%3BThese%20two%20things%20will%20get%20used%20together.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMicrosoft%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20in%20a%20press%20release%20that%20its%20topological%20superconductor%20is%C2%A0a%20new%20material%20that%20isn't%20solid%2C%20liquid%2C%20or%20gas%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ewhich%20the%20company%20fabricated%20atom%20by%20atom.%20Where%20many%20familiar%20electronic%20devices%20rely%20on%20the%20raw%20material%20silicon%20in%20their%20semiconductors%2C%20Microsoft%20said%20in%20peer-reviewed%20findings%20released%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D2fee788c90c1f304dc53153501ca36853216e7911ca88bb15211fe38247cb42d%26postID%3D67b63b8c0060db112e167873%26postSlug%3Dsatya-nadella-microsoft-new-majorana-chip-quantum-breakthrough-state-matter-2025-2%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.nature.com%252Farticles%252Fs41586-024-08445-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENature%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20its%20topological%20superconductor%20is%20a%20path%20forward%20for%20quantum%20computing%20to%20produce%20more%20stable%20qubits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETroy%20Nelson%2C%20the%20Chief%20Technology%20Officer%20at%20Lastwall%2C%20a%20cybersecurity%20provider%20of%20quantum%20resilient%20technology%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%2C%20since%20the%20behavior%20of%20quantum%20systems%20is%20often%20hard%20to%20prove%20due%20to%20the%20unstable%20nature%20of%20qubits%2C%20he'd%20like%20to%20see%20more%20real-world%20testing%20to%20confirm%20Microsoft's%20findings%2C%20but%20he's%20%26quot%3Bmore%20on%20the%20optimistic%20side%20of%20cautiously%20optimistic%26quot%3B%20about%20the%20company's%20announcement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20they've%20done%20is%20they've%20created%20a%20new%20foundation%20that%20we%20can%20build%20off%20of%2C%26quot%3B%20Nelson%20said.%20%26quot%3BNow%20we%20need%20to%20solve%20the%20production%20problems%20like%20the%20economies%20of%20scale%20and%20bringing%20costs%20down.%20But%20I%20see%20what%20they%20produced%20here%20as%20a%20new%20road%20map.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMicrosoft's%20new%20topological%20architecture%C2%A0was%C2%A0used%20to%20develop%20its%20Majorana%201%20processor%2C%20offering%C2%A0what%20the%20company%2C%20in%20its%20press%20release%2C%20called%C2%A0%26quot%3Ba%20clear%20path%20to%20fit%20a%20million%20qubits%20on%20a%20single%20chip%20that%20can%20fit%20in%20the%20palm%20of%20one's%20hand.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Microsoft's%20Majorana%201%20chip%20in%20the%20palm%20of%20a%20person's%20hand.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67b687d8eb4be2fff9a512d0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221334%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMicrosoft's%20Majorana%201%20chip%20is%20the%20first%20quantum%20computing%20chip%20powered%20by%20topological%20qubits.%3Cp%3EMicrosoft%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20needed%20threshold%20for%20quantum%20computers%20to%20deliver%20transformative%2C%20real-world%20solutions%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20breaking%20down%20microplastics%20into%20harmless%20byproducts%20or%20inventing%20self-healing%20materials%20for%20construction%2C%20manufacturing%20or%20healthcare%2C%26quot%3B%20Microsoft's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.microsoft.com%2Fsource%2Ffeatures%2Fai%2Fmicrosofts-majorana-1-chip-carves-new-path-for-quantum-computing%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epress%20release%3C%2Fa%3E%20reads.%20%26quot%3BAll%20the%20world's%20current%20computers%20operating%20together%20can't%20do%20what%20a%20one-million-qubit%20quantum%20computer%20will%20be%20able%20to%20do.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENelson%20said%20Microsoft's%20topological%20breakthrough%2C%20if%20it%20can%20be%20replicated%20by%20other%20researchers%20in%20the%20field%2C%20will%20be%20a%20turning%20point%20that%20shortens%20the%20timeline%20for%20developing%20fully%20functional%20quantum%20computers%20to%20just%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20we%20really%20can%20print%20topoconductor%20to%20chips%20the%20size%20of%20your%20hand%2C%20that's%20just%20as%20revolutionary%20as%20the%20silicon%20transistor%2C%26quot%3B%20Nelson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMicrosoft's%20stock%20rose%201.25%25%20on%20Wednesday%20following%20the%20announcement%20of%20its%20new%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-google-quantum-willow-chip-breakthrough-big-deal-researchers-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Equantum%20chip%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Microsoft's%20Majorana%201%20chip%20doesn't%20mean%20commercially%20useful%20quantum%20computing%20is%20right%20around%20the%20corner%2C%20it%20is%20the%20latest%20in%20a%20series%20of%20significant%20advancements%20in%20the%20field%20that%20leads%20some%20researchers%20to%20believe%20more%20widespread%2C%20commercial%20adoption%20will%20come%20sooner%20than%20previously%20expected.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20December%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-unveiled-quantum-computer-chip-willow-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EGoogle%20unveiled%20Willow%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20its%20new%20quantum%20chip%2C%20which%20the%20company%20says%20can%20perform%20a%20standard%20benchmark%20computation%20in%20under%20five%20minutes%20%E2%80%94%20a%20task%20that%20would%20take%20the%20current%20fastest%20supercomputers%2010%20septillion%20years%20to%20complete%3B%20a%20timeframe%20that%20exceeds%20the%20age%20of%20the%20universe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20not%20everyone%20is%20convinced.%20Quantum%20stocks%20tumbled%20in%20January%20after%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fquantum-computing-stocks-jensen-huang-nvidia-ces-rigetti-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENvidia%20CEO%20Jensen%20Huang%3C%2Fa%3E%20suggested%20we're%20still%2020%20years%20away%20from%20the%20technology%20being%20%26quot%3Bvery%20useful.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsatya-nadella-microsoft-new-majorana-chip-quantum-breakthrough-state-matter-2025-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740016461000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67b64425