t's%20my%20understanding%20that%20more%20people%20get%20dumped%20on%20Valentine's%20Day%20than%20any%20other%20day%20of%20the%20year%2C%20other%20than%20New%20Year's%20Eve.%20So%20if%20you're%20part%20of%20that%20cohort%2C%20please%20accept%20my%20condolences.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIndeed%2C%20Arnott%20knows%20that%20being%20there%20for%20those%20down%20on%20their%20luck%2C%20at%20least%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20stocks%2C%20can%20be%20quite%20profitable.%20Arnott's%20specialty%20is%20creating%20alternative%20indexes%2C%20and%20this%20group%20of%20stocks%20he's%20put%20together%20%E2%80%94%20the%20Research%20Affiliates%20Deletions%20ETF%20(NIXT)%2C%20which%20was%20launched%20in%20September%20%E2%80%94%20aims%20to%20capitalize%20on%20the%20rebound%20that%20companies%20kicked%20out%20of%20major%20indexes%20tend%20to%20see%20in%20the%20years%20after%20their%20deletions.%20Those%20indexes%20include%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%2C%20the%20Nasdaq%20100%2C%20and%20the%20Russell%201000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBased%20on%20the%20performance%20of%20the%20fund's%20top%20holdings%20over%20the%20last%20year%2C%20Arnott%20appears%20to%20be%20on%20to%20something.%20The%20vast%20majority%20of%20the%20fund's%20top%2025%20holdings%20have%20smashed%20the%20market%20over%20the%20last%2012%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20tracks%20with%20history.%20According%20to%20Arnott's%20research%20of%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20and%20Russell%201000%20deletions%20from%201991-2018%20and%20Nasdaq%20100%20deletions%20from%202004-2018%2C%20stocks%20that%20get%20removed%20from%20the%20above%20indexes%20have%20beaten%20their%20respective%20index%20over%20the%20following%20five%20years%20by%20an%20average%20of%2028%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20happens%20because%20the%20stocks%20are%20already%20usually%20trading%20at%20a%20discount%2C%20he%20said%2C%20which%20is%20why%20they're%20kicked%20out%20of%20their%20index%20to%20begin%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20average%2C%20these%20stocks%20are%20down%20by%20over%2050%25%20in%20the%20year%20before%20they're%20deleted%2C%26quot%3B%20Arnott%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EArnott%20doesn't%20include%20every%20stock%20that's%20taken%20out%20of%20its%20index%2C%20however.%20If%20they're%20in%20the%20bottom%20quintile%20of%20deleted%20stocks%20in%20terms%20of%20quality%20factors%20like%20their%20profit%20margins%20and%20debt-to-equity%20ratio%2C%20he%20leaves%20them%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBelow%2C%20we've%20included%20the%20top%2025%20stocks%20in%20the%20fund%20by%20weighting.%20The%20full%20list%20of%20138%20holdings%20can%20be%20found%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fetfarchitect.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fcompliance%2Fetf%2Fpart_f%2FNIXT_part_f_q1.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E1.%20Lumen%20Technologies%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221646%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22lumn%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67b4ed0f6630eb10385ce92a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221364%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EMarkets%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETicker%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Flumn-stock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELUMN%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWeight%20in%20NIXT%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%202.63%25%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPerformance%20last%2012%20months%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20223.5%25%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E2.%20Affirm%20Holdings%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221612%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22afrm%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67b4ed516630eb10385ce93d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221332%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EMarkets%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETicker%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Fafrm-stock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAFRM%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E