ked%20Up%20History%20With%20Two%20MICHELIN%20Stars%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Cem%3Egobi%20parantha%20%3C%2Fem%3Eat%20restaurant%20Gaa%20%E2%80%94%20a%20bespoke%20dining%20experience%20in%20Bangkok%2C%20Thailand%2C%20curated%20by%20the%20eponymous%20Chef%20Garima%20Arora%20%E2%80%94%20has%20a%20separate%20fanbase.%20Calling%20it%20a%20dish%20would%20do%20it%20a%20disservice.%20Let%E2%80%99s%20instead%20describe%20it%20as%20a%20marriage%20between%20unleavened%20flatbread%20and%20savoury%2C%20spiced%20cauliflower%20filling%3B%20a%20ceremony%20that%20is%20graced%20by%20dollops%20of%20butter%2C%20the%20recipe%20for%20which%20was%20born%20in%20a%20particular%20kitchen%20cupboard%20in%20Delhi%2C%20where%20Chef%20Garima%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3Edadi%20%3C%2Fem%3E(paternal%20grandmother)%20lived.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20recalls%20how%20the%20cupboard%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3Ejhali%20%3C%2Fem%3E(lattice)%20door%20allowed%20passersby%20a%20view%20of%20thick%20cream%20fermenting%20into%20butter%20in%20real%20time.%20She%20could%20spend%20hours%20feasting%20her%20eyes%20on%20it.%20The%20recipe%20for%20the%20cauliflower%20mix%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20comes%20from%20her%20%3Cem%3Enani%20%3C%2Fem%3E(maternal%20grandmother).%20Guests%20at%20Gaa%20love%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F369414%2Fparatha-spots-in-delhi-moolchand-parantha-paranthe-wali-gali-shaheen-bagh-40-foota%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20%3Cem%3Egobi%20parantha%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3C%2Fa%3Efor%20its%20simplicity%3B%20but%20for%20Chef%20Garima%2C%20it%20resembles%20an%20umbilical%20link%20to%20her%20roots.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlbeit%20it%20isn%E2%80%99t%20her%20first%20instance%20of%20taking%20the%20soul%20of%20Indian%20food%20to%20a%20global%20culinary%20dais.%20For%20Chef%20Garima%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20been%20a%20constant%20endeavour%20since%20her%20student%20days%20at%20the%20prestigious%20Le%20Cordon%20Bleu%20in%20Paris%2C%20fol