0variety%20to%20grow%20well%20in%20different%20climates%20across%20the%20country.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20thrives%20in%20all%20conditions%20%E2%80%94%20mountainous%2C%20plains%2C%20and%20everywhere%20in%20between%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Mehra.%20The%20individual%20grain%20count%20per%20stalk%20reached%2050-80%2C%20far%20exceeding%20the%20normal%2020-25%20grains%20in%20traditional%20varieties.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%224678180483%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVinita%20Singh%2C%20a%2060-year-old%20farmer%20from%20Uttarakhand%2C%20found%20out%20about%20the%20new%20wheat%20variety%20after%20reading%20about%20Mehra%20in%20the%20local%20news%20circuit.%20She%20decided%20to%20give%20it%20a%20try%20and%20found%20it%20to%20be%20highly%20effective%20for%20her%20own%20farm%20as%20well.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%20makes%20Narendra%2009%20wheat%20special%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20and%20her%20son%20farm%20the%20wheat%20on%20six%20acres%20of%20land.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20difference%20in%20the%20variety%20of%20wheat%20is%20that%20we%20see%20each%20acre%20producing%202%2C800%20to%202%2C900%20kgs%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F393883%2Fchokhone-krichena-dianthe-floriculture-mao-manipur-empowering-farmer%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecommercial%20farming%20practices%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20is%20significantly%20more%20than%20most%20crops%20grown%20in%20the%20region.%20We%20grow%20them%20organically%20as%20well%2C%20and%20there%20the%20quality%20of%20our%20produce%20is%20better%20than%20many%20others%20in%20the%20area%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20new%20wheat%20variety%20req